column5: I went out on Thursday for another try at some Lake O Pike and got a couple smaller fish and one fat 32 incher. It was the fattest Pike I've ever caught. Usually I grab pike behind the head but I couldn't fit my hand around this one and had to scoop him onto shore with my arms. Amazing fight, when I released him he completely soaked me! Can't wait to see this guy at 40+ inches! Too bad it was a blurry pic.   -Ben
Definitely a beauty chunky fish. Wish our fish were still chubby haha.  Glad you got out!
Nice Pike. Hopefully I get my first soon!
fished that elbow last fall. nice chunk pike .congrats.
Awesome gator Ben Great job and thanks for sharing!!! Leechman
nice pike...any pike at 40+ would be good
Great job.  You're off to a great start this season.
